videos.description: 1H (15:24) TXSO Derrick Griffin made Dunk. Assisted by Dulani Robinson.
videos.headline: D. Griffin made Dunk. Assisted by D. Robinson.

videos.description: Cincinnati moving the ball around, they eventually get it to Tre Scott, who finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Cincinnati turns nice passing into a Tre Scott dunk

videos.description: Demontrae Jefferson lobs a  pass off the backboard for Derrick Griffin, who finishes with the thunderous two-handed dunk for Texas Southern.
videos.headline: Texas Southern's Griffin slams it home with authority

videos.description: Cincinnati taking its time with the ball, Justin Jenifer eventually gets it and passes off to Tre Scott, who finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Scott dunks it again for Cincinnati

videos.description: Cainan McClelland flips over Tre Scott as Scott goes to make the basket.
videos.headline: C. McClelland filps over T. Scott.
